@project epsd2
@lang sux
@name epsd2/sux

@entry a [water] N
@bases a 
@form a /a #~
@sense N water
@end entry

@entry* a šaga šu dug [beget] V/t
@parts a[water]N šag[heart]N šu[hand]N dug[speak]V/t
@sense V/t to beget, father
@end entry

@entry dug [speak] V/t
@bases da; da-g·a (da-ga); de₂; du; du-g·a; du-q·a; dug; dug-ga; dug₄ (dag₅, du₁₁); du₁₀; du₁₁-du₁₁ (dug₄-dug₄); du₁₁-du₁₁{+du-du}; du₁₂; du₁₂-du₁₂; du₃; du₇; du₈; du₉-du₉; e; su-ga; ti; tu; {+da}dug₄ (da-k·a); {+du-ug}dug₄; {+du}dug₄ (du-k·a)
@sense V/t to speak, talk, say
@sense V/t to order
@sense V/t to do, perform
@sense V/t to negotiate
@end entry

@entry šag [heart] N
@bases {+ša₂-ga}šag₄; {kuš}šag₄; {tug₂}šag₄; {urud}šag₄; {uzu}šag₄; {ŋeš}šag₄; {ŋeš}šag₄-šag₄; ša; šag₃; šag₄ (ša₃); šag₄-ga; šag₄-šag₄; šak; ša₃-ga-ni
@sense N heart
@sense N inner body, womb, belly, intestines
